Last month, texts sent by the murdered wife to Coello were revealed.

Prosecutors say Coello, 41, flew into a violent rage after Ms Adovasio told him in text messages she wanted a divorce because she suspected him of cheating.

In one, she told him that if he wanted to 'live his life as a single guy’ he should 'take his s**t' and get out.

The texts were read at a pre-trial hearing on a defense motion to keep the jury from seeing the confrontational texts.

